Germany’s SPD Want a Capital Tax to Help Poor, Handelsblatt Says

-- B y   H o l g e r   E l f e s
-- 
2011-05-07T08:59:33Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-07/germany-s-spd-want-a-capital-tax-to-help-poor-handelsblatt-says.html
Germany ’s Social  Democratic Party 
wants to reintroduce a capital tax to narrow the gap between
rich and poor in the country,  Handelsblatt  reported today,
citing Joachim Poss, the opposition party’s deputy Bundestag
group leader.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Holger Elfes in Dusseldorf at 
 helfes@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Celeste Perri at   cperri@bloomberg.net . 